Installation
====================

This project plots graphs based on time series within HDF5. It needs HDF5 version >= 1.8.2 . You can download it from
http://www.hdfgroup.org . Another requirement is libqwt5. The program will not work with libqwt6.

After the installation proceed with the following steps.

1. Checkout from git
--------------------

If not already done, checkout the git tree
# git clone https://github.com/mbsim-env/hdf5serie.git


2. Run AutoTools
----------------

# aclocal
# autoheader
# libtoolize -c --force
# autoconf
# automake -a -c --force


3. Proceed with configure
-------------------------

See file INSTALL.
